LSC Lithium

LSC has assembled a large portfolio of high-quality lithium brine projects  in Argentina and is focused on becoming a significant player in the supply of high quality lithium product to global markets.
LSC has amassed a large portfolio of prospective lithium rich salars in Argentina.Majority of land holdings are on high-quality salars in the provinces of Salta and Jujuy.Six major development stage lithium projects with a total of ~300,000 hectares of exploration properties. Exploration and development properties include Pozuelos, Pastos Grandes, Salinas Grandes (Salta), Salinas Grandes (Jujuy), Rio Grande and Jama.Properties are located in the “Lithium Triangle,” an area covering Argentina, Bolivia and Chile where the world’s most abundant lithium brine deposits are found.Focused on becoming a significant supplier of high quality lithium product to global markets from its extensive holdings in Argentina.Exclusive access in Argentina to game-changing, low-cost processing technology.


















