			Company Description 


			LSC Lithium Corp. engages in the exploration activities. It involves in the identification and evaluation of assets or a business for potential acquisition or participation in a business. It currently operates a lithium brine projects such as Salar Rio Grande Tenements, Salar Pastos Grandes Tenement...
		


                LSC Lithium Corp. engages in the exploration activities. It involves in the identification and evaluation of assets or a business for potential acquisition or participation in a business. It currently operates a lithium brine projects such as Salar Rio Grande Tenements, Salar Pastos Grandes Tenements, Salar Salinas Grandes Tenements, and Salar Jama Tenements located Argentina, Bolivia, and Chile. The company was founded on October 30, 2009 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
            




